text: Holly Hobbie & Friends Is a series of animated specials produced by Nickelodeon and American Greetings It is the series to star the Holly Hobbie doll, albeit redesigned from her traditional look. The specials aired on both Nickelodeon's Nick Jr. Block and the separate Noggin channel country singer LeAnn Rimes sang the theme song Category:Nickelodeon television series
title: Holly Hobbie & Friends
